    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so empty now. like after 10 years, the person who was my whole world is just... gone. i wake up and for a split second i forget, then it hits me all over again and i just cant breathe. i dont see a point to any of this anymore. there's no version of the future that doesn't feel like a lie.",
